translated: Åstradsson, Johan Otto, battalion veterinarian, district veterinarian, Rockneby, b. 23/5/99 in Rödinge, Malmöh. 1st marriage 27 with Lisa Hallström. Children: Lans Ove b. 28, Anna-Lisa b. 29, Nils Bertil b. 32. — High school graduate in Ystad 17, veterinary graduate 24. Battalion veterinarian in FVK reserve 27, district veterinarian in Rockneby district 34. Awarded the Order of the Polar Star, 4th class with a sword.
